<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 A JUST and NECESSARY WAR  
 &HT;     (This has already moved to clients of The New York Times
op-eds. To publish as a special one-shot article, please contact
your New York Times Syndicate representative:
