   &UR; WASHINGTON &LR;  (``w'' code)
</P>
<P>
   CONGRESS (Washington) _ Despite Speaker Dennis Hastert's promise
to have three spending bills finished by Memorial Day, nothing has
moved forward, and paralysis on the Hill this early in the session
shows how difficult real action will be on real issues. By Alison
Mitchell and Tim Weiner.
</P>
