<P>
   &UR; CONFLICT IN THE BALKANS &LR;   &UR; (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   YUGOSLAVIA (Budapest) _ Yugoslavia briefly seizes six NATO
soldiers over the border in Bosnia in the latest incursion of
neighboring states. By Kevin Cullen and Susan Milligan. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
