<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-28 19:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5487 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BIZ-5-QUESTIONS-ART-$     05-28 0825
