husband, went berserk one night and stabbed his wife 44 times and
then held her head in their swimming pool when she made the fatal
mistake of interrupting him while he was sleepwalking, his attorney
contends. Prosecutors contend it was premeditated murder. The trial
continues, although there wa no session Friday. The Republic
